 \sum\limits_{i=0}^{\infty} a_i(b_i - c_i) = \sum\limits_{i=0}^{\infty} (a_ib_i - a_ic_i) =\sum\limits_{i=0}^{\infty} a_ib_i - \sum\limits_{i=0}^{\infty} a_ic_i 
\sum_{i=1}^\infty a_i=\lim_{n\to\infty}(a_1+\ldots+a_n).
\lim_{n\to\infty}a_n(b_n-c_n)=\lim_{n\to\infty}a_n b_n-\lim_{n\to\infty}a_n c_n,
\sum_{i=0}^\infty a_i b_i
\sum_{i=0}^\infty b_i c_i 
 \sum_{i=0}^\infty a_i (b_i - c_i)
\sum_{i=0}^\infty |a_i b_i|
